OL,3,CPolice officer accused of rape and
OL,4,Csexual assualt
OL,6,FA West Yorkshire police officer is due
OL,7,Fto appear in court charged with rape
OL,8,Fand three counts of sexual assault.
OL,10,FDetective Constable Dan Livesley, 48,
OL,11,Fwho is based in the Bradford District,
OL,12,Fis due to appear before York
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday 30 June.
OL,15,FIn a statement, police confirmed that
OL,16,Fthe charges relate to offences
OL,17,Freported to have occurred while the
OL,18,Fofficer was off duty.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
